<p class="research-intro">
  Transmission network: every node is a macro indicator from FRED, every edge is a 60-month rolling
  correlation between two YoY-transformed (or level) series. Edge color encodes sign (green &gt; 0, red &lt; 0)
  and width encodes magnitude. Arrows appear when peak cross-correlation has a non-zero lag of at least 2 months
  and agrees in sign with the rolling estimate. Click a node to drill into the
  <a href="/core/econ/">Indicator Library</a>; click an edge to open the pair in the
  <a href="/core/macro/research.html">Pair Explorer</a>.
</p>

<section class="controls">
  <div class="control">
    <label for="net-window">Correlation window</label>
    <select id="net-window">
      <option value="36">36 months</option>
      <option value="60" selected>60 months</option>
      <option value="120">120 months</option>
    </select>
  </div>
  <div class="control">
    <label for="net-min-corr">Hide weak edges (|r| &lt;)</label>
    <select id="net-min-corr">
      <option value="0">show all</option>
      <option value="0.2" selected>0.20</option>
      <option value="0.3">0.30</option>
      <option value="0.5">0.50</option>
    </select>
  </div>
  <div class="control">
    <label for="net-show-lags">Lead-lag arrows</label>
    <select id="net-show-lags">
      <option value="1" selected>show</option>
      <option value="0">hide</option>
    </select>
  </div>
  <div class="control" style="justify-content: flex-end;">
    <label>&nbsp;</label>
    <button id="net-reset" class="theme-toggle" style="margin-left:0">Reset layout</button>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="panel">
  <div id="rec-bar" class="rec-bar">
    <span class="rec-bar-count">Recession composite: <strong id="rec-count">&mdash;</strong>/5 signals triggered</span>
    <span class="rec-bar-dots" id="rec-dots"></span>
    <span class="rec-bar-tier" id="rec-tier">&mdash;</span>
    <span style="color: var(--muted)" id="rec-asof">&nbsp;</span>
    <a href="/core/econ/recession.html" class="rec-bar-link">Open full composite &rarr;</a>
  </div>

  <div class="net-legend" id="net-legend"></div>

  <div class="net-grid">
    <div class="net-wrap">
      <svg id="net" viewBox="0 0 680 600" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" aria-label="Macro indicator transmission network">
        <defs>
          <marker id="arrPos" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="9" refY="5" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" orient="auto-start-reverse">
            <path d="M0 0 L10 5 L0 10 z" fill="var(--green)"/>
          </marker>
          <marker id="arrNeg" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="9" refY="5" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" orient="auto-start-reverse">
            <path d="M0 0 L10 5 L0 10 z" fill="var(--red)"/>
          </marker>
        </defs>
        <g id="edges-g"></g>
        <g id="lags-g"></g>
        <g id="nodes-g"></g>
      </svg>
      <div id="net-status" class="net-status">Loading FRED series and computing correlations&hellip;</div>
    </div>

    <aside class="net-detail" id="net-detail">
      <h3 id="nd-title">Click a node to inspect</h3>
      <div class="nd-sub" id="nd-sub">Hover highlights the neighborhood. Click a node to pin its detail; click any tag below to walk the graph.</div>
      <div id="nd-body" style="display:none">
        <div class="nd-grid">
          <div>
            <div class="nd-row"><span>Latest</span><span id="nd-val">&mdash;</span></div>
            <div class="nd-row"><span>YoY</span><span id="nd-yoy">&mdash;</span></div>
            <div class="nd-row"><span>As-of</span><span id="nd-asof">&mdash;</span></div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="nd-row"><span>Sector</span><span id="nd-sec">&mdash;</span></div>
            <div class="nd-row"><span>FRED</span><span id="nd-src">&mdash;</span></div>
            <div class="nd-row"><span>Edges</span><span id="nd-deg">&mdash;</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a class="nd-cta" id="nd-cta-drill" href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open indicator drilldown &rarr;</a>
        <div class="nd-links" id="nd-links"></div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>

  <div class="net-foot-grid">
    <div>
      <h4>Reading the network</h4>
      <p>
        Edges measure the trailing-window Pearson correlation on monthly observations.
        Series in levels (rates, spreads, %) stay in levels; index series (CPI, GDP, IP, S&amp;P, etc.) are YoY-transformed.
        Arrows show peak cross-correlation lag in [-12, +12] months &mdash; the leader is upstream of the arrow.
        Lag arrows are suppressed when the peak's sign disagrees with the rolling-window sign (typically a regime artifact).
      </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h4>Recession-composite signals</h4>
      <p>
        Nodes ringed in amber are part of the live <a href="/core/econ/recession.html">5-signal recession composite</a>:
        Sahm Indicator, 10Y-3M Curve, HY OAS, UNRATE 6mo &Delta;, NFP 3mo avg.
        Triggered signals turn red. The bar at the top mirrors the landing-page composite and is computed
        from the same series via <code>recession-core.js</code>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <span>Data: FRED via <code>/api/fred</code>. Computations done client-side.</span>
  <span id="last-updated">&mdash;</span>
</footer>

